{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-share-feedback/task-57","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-share-feedback","challengeType":19,"description":"","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Vitenzi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">guess</span> na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">feel</span> koristi se za prikaz komentara na veoma nestabilan način.</p>\n<p>U ovim slučajevima, wakati <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Present Simple</span> se koristi umesto vremena <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Present Continuous</span> jer su <span class=\"highlighted-text\">guess</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">feel</span> glagoli stanja, koji opisuju mentalno stanje umesto radnji. Zato kažemo <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I guess</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I feel</span>, a ne <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I'm guessing</span> ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I'm feeling</span> kada izražavamo mišljenja.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">To guess</span> znači pogađati ili doći do zaključka bez potpunog sigurnosti, dok <span class=\"highlighted-text\">to feel</span> ukazuje lično mišljenje ili osećanje. Na primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">I guess he'll be late because of traffic.</span> - To znači da govornik misli da će kasnuti, ali nije siguran.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">I feel that this decision is the best for the team.</span> - Ovo znači da govornik veruje da je ovo pravi izbor.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>","helpCategory":"English","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte audio odgovor na pitanje ispod.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-share-feedback/task-57"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Prema Lisi, što mnogo rasprava može uzrokovati?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Može da radi efikasnije.</p>","feedback":"<p>Lisa predlaže da previše rasprave može odložiti stvari.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Može pomoći timu da završe svoj posao brže.</p>","feedback":"<p>Lisa kaže da previše razgovora može uzrokovati kašnjenje.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Može eliminisati potrebu za radom.</p>","feedback":"<p>Lisa nije predložila da debata zauzima mesto stvarnog rada.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Može da ukloni vreme potrebno za završetak stvarnog zadatka.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null}],"solution":4}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","characters":[{"character":"Lisa","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"B1_8-2.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":32.16,"finishTimestamp":38.1},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Lisa","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Lisa","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.92,"dialogue":{"text":"I guess you're right.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lisa","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":2.16,"finishTime":4.36,"dialogue":{"text":"I just feel that if we focus too much on debating,","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lisa","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":4.72,"finishTime":6.94,"dialogue":{"text":"we won't have enough time to get the actual work done.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lisa","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":7.44,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"b1-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 57","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-share-feedback","dashedName":"task-57","certification":"b1-english-for-developers","disableLoopProte